Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是來挖墓的 到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭被切下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被防腐處理過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是胸口被刺而死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過防腐處理後才被割下頭顱的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有頭部腐爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去問一下管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意思犯人就是墓地的管理人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是叫你去問 到底是誰搬來了這具屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南無阿彌陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是東洋的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祈禱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那具屍體 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是穿著整齊的官員們搬來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 我要回劇院了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出就快要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
